      "content": "it's just that the drooping isn't really going away, and i'm feeling kinda dizzy too. are you sure it's just a migraine? i'm kinda nervous to go to the er if it's not an emergency since it's so expensive. is there anything else i can do for the face thing besides the sumatriptan?",
