      "content": "it's just so hard to justify a hospital trip right now. i read online that sometimes intense migraines can cause temporary facial numbness or weakness. if i just take a couple of extra sumatriptan to see if the pain stops, and then wait an hour to see if the face stuff goes away on its own, would that be alright? i really don't want to go to the er if it isn't 100% necessary.",
